The son to the late Cabinet Minister Mbiyu Koinange is dead following a road accident along Mau Narok-Nakuru road. The car which David Waiganjo Koinange was driving was involved in an accident on Thursday evening while on his way home. According to Njoro Sub-County Police Commander Mohammed Huka, the accident occurred at around 9pm as he was on his way to Muthera farm. The Police Commander added that the deceased was in his Range Rover alone when the accident occurred. Huka said one of the car's tyres burst and the car rolled over. More to followâ€¦ 